CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FEvidence from senior figures including
OL,7,Fformer top Foreign Office(FCDO)
OL,8,Fmandarin Sir Philip Barton about Lord
OL,9,FMandelson's vetting for the role has
OL,10,Fthe potential to throw up further
OL,11,Fchallenges for Sir Keir's position at
OL,12,Fa committee hearing early on Tuesday.
OL,14,FA large-scale effort to shore up
OL,15,Fbackbench support was under way on
OL,16,FMonday night, with former Labour prime
OL,17,Fminister Gordon Brown also urging the
OL,18,Fparty to back the Prime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
