PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FAllies of Sir Keir appeared confident
OL,7,Fthat a mass rebellion was off the
OL,8,Fcards as he told a packed meeting of
OL,9,Fthe Parliamentary Labour Party (PLP):
OL,10,F"When we stick together and fight
OL,11,Ftogether we are so much stronger."
OL,13,FHe sought to dismiss the Commons bid
OL,14,Fto refer him to the committee which
OL,15,Fended Boris Johnson's political career
OL,16,Fas a "stunt" by political opponents
OL,17,Fintent on inflicting damage before the
OL,18,FMay elections.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@bO]xD@FOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FIt is understood Labour MPs are being
OL,7,Fwhipped to reject the motion after
OL,8,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,9,Fallowed a vote on the issue on Tuesday
OL,10,Ffollowing requests from Tory leader
OL,11,FKemi Badenoch and other senior MPs.
OL,13,FSir Keir told the PLP: "I have
OL,14,Fresponsibility for being totally
OL,15,Ftransparent with you, with Parliament
OL,16,Fand the British public.
OL,18,F"I take that very seriously as well.
OL,19,FBut this is not about a lack of
OL,20,Ftransparency.
OL,26,@uD@XOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,F"This is a political stunt by our
OL,7,Fopponents who want to bring us down,
OL,8,Fobscure our message, stop us getting
OL,9,Fon with our work.
OL,11,F"And the timing tells you everything,
OL,12,Fnine days before local elections."
OL,14,FHe said the Conservatives had put
OL,15,Fforward "totally baseless" and
OL,16,F"absolutely ridiculous" accusations
OL,17,Fagainst him and insisted the motion on
OL,18,FTuesday was "pure politics", adding:
OL,19,F"We need to stand together against it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@bO]wD@IOUwD@ZO]xD@AOUxD@
OL,26,AWO]zD@MOUzD@[O]{D@AOU{D@gO]
