OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FThe Government also took the unusual
OL,7,Fstep on Monday of publishing a letter
OL,8,Ffrom former cabinet secretary Sir
OL,9,FChris Wormald to the Prime Minister,
OL,10,Fin which he said he had concluded the
OL,11,F"appropriate processes were followed"
OL,12,Fin both the appointment and sacking of
OL,13,Fthe peer.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
