PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FSir Keir has also faced questions for
OL,7,Finsisting to MPs that "no pressure
OL,8,Fexisted whatsoever in relation to this
OL,9,Fcase" after former top Foreign Office
OL,10,Fofficial Sir Olly Robbins said there
OL,11,Fhad been "constant chasing" from No 10
OL,12,Fwhile checks were taking place for the
OL,13,Fambassadorship.
OL,15,FFormer permanent secretary Sir Olly's
OL,16,Fclaims were echoed in written evidence
OL,17,Fto the Foreign Affairs Committee
OL,18,Fpublished on Monday evening from
OL,19,Fanother key figure in the security
OL,20,Fprocess.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@EO]sD@JOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777345462
OL,3,CStarmer faces crunch vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row
OL,6,FAccording to a letter from the Foreign
OL,7,FOffice drafted in consultation with
OL,8,FIan Collard, who was head of security
OL,9,Fin the department, the official said
OL,10,Fhe "felt pressure to deliver a rapid
OL,11,Foutcome" to the clearance procedure.
OL,13,FThis was in light of "regular contact
OL,14,Ffrom No 10 to the FCDO (permanent
OL,15,Funder-secretary's) office," the letter
OL,16,Fsaid, although Mr Collard did not
OL,17,Fpersonally speak to Downing Street
OL,18,Fcolleagues and "does not assess that
OL,19,Fthis pressure influenced professional
OL,20,Fjudgment that was reached by himself
OL,21,For his team".
OL,26,@rD@DOUsD@HO]uD@VOUwD@[O]zD@POU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
